title: #92Noon! Charch in for PA/Gleeman/Krawczynski
description: Full show! Charch is in for PA today and he wants to talk about sex, ba-by. Specifically how to talk to your kids about it without making it weird. Aaron Gleeman is in studio to talk Twins, PA calls in from NOLA ahead of tonight's first preseason game, and Jonny Athletic in studio to discuss the champions of the Target Center, and no it's not the Twolves, it's the E-sports team.
